<div class='spoiler'>
<a class="spoiler" href="/questions/417746-possible-spoiler-if-you-have-finished">This question contains spoilers...</a>
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[Possible SPOILER:<br /><br />If you have finished the book, let's discuss on this thread what you think happened in the end. Did she get caught or not? Give your reasons.. <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
